  "categorySlug": "organisational-roll-out",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Description of the clean-up flow</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Here is a short description of Data &amp; More's best practice clean-up flow.</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p><em>In English:</em></p>\n<p>This is our best practice recommendation for the clean-up flow.</p>\n<p>Any file older than 3 months, that contains personally identifiable data, will be notified to end users in a clean-up report that is sent out quarterly.&nbsp; They will have a 3-month period where they can decide to exempt a certain file from the automatic clean-up report and process. If there is no exception on a file, it will be deleted after that 3-month period.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Note: It is possible to exempt data from being part of the clean-up process (before sending a clean-up report or after the clean-up report has been sent out). The options can be folders named e.g. \"private\", \"to be kept\" or other names. The more unique, the better. The content of those folders can be exempt. What should be exempt is part of the decision that need to be made as part of the implementation process. It is also possible to exempt AD groups or create a new AD group, where it is possible to for the customer, on short notice, to put in users accounts that should be exempt.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>High level overview of the clean-up process:</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"367\" style=\"width: 688px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=367&amp;name=image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png\" width=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png?width=344&amp;height=184&amp;name=image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=367&amp;name=image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png?width=1032&amp;height=551&amp;name=image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png?width=1376&amp;height=734&amp;name=image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png?width=1720&amp;height=918&amp;name=image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png?width=2064&amp;height=1101&amp;name=image-png-Nov-14-2023-11-52-46-9681-AM.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
